<section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
        <h1>
            <%= brandName.toUpperCase() %> Official Site
        </h1>
        <p>Welcome to the official <%= brandName %> portal. Your #1 source for free live sports streaming.</p>
        <div class="hero-filters">
            <a href="/football/" class="hero-btn">Football Streams</a>
            <a href="/nfl/" class="hero-btn">NFL Streams</a>
            <a href="/nba/" class="hero-btn">NBA Streams</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="container">
    <div class="brand-content-card">
        <h2>About <%= brandName %>
        </h2>
        <p>
            <%= brandName %> (often misspelled as Footybite, Footybyte, or Fotybyte) is a premier sports aggregation
                platform. We provide fans with the best high-definition links for every major sporting event.
        </p>
        <p>Our mission is to make sports accessible to everyone, everywhere, for free. By bookmarking the official <%=
                brandName %> site, you ensure you always have access to the latest live streams.</p>

        <h3>Why fans trust <%= brandName %>?</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Reliability:</strong> Links are verified and updated every hour.</li>
            <li><strong>Quality:</strong> We prioritize HD streams with minimal buffering.</li>
            <li><strong>Safety:</strong> Our platform is optimized for a clean, fast user experience.</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="brand-cta">
            <a href="/" class="reset-btn">Go to Live Feed</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>